Package: xfce4-windowck-plugin
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, xfce4-panel (>= 4.10), libwnck22
Description: Xfce panel plugin which allows to put the maximized window title on the panel.
 This plugin for Xfce panel show the title of the focused maximized window,
 this allows to remove the title bar for maximized window.
